==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-unc}}

# Any [[leftover]] waste or [[scraps]] or [[material]] deemed [[useless]] or disposable.

:*(The designation of an item as garbage can be highly [[subjective]] and subject to change. An item once thought to be garbage may in fact prove (if not treated as garbage and disposed) to have priceless value such as [[Placenta|afterbirth]] which, along with the [[Umbilical cord|umbilical cord]], constitute a valuable material resource for [[stem cell]] and other [[biological]] research.)

